---
const recruitPoints = [
  '完全週休2日制',
  '平均月収30万円以上',
  '個室サロン・少人数制',
  '残業少なめ',
  '有給消化率90%以上',
  '未経験OK・研修充実',
];
---

<section class="recruit section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="recruit-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">RECRUIT</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">一緒に働く仲間を募集中</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">働きやすさを大切に、プライベートも充実</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="recruit-points">
        {recruitPoints.map((point) => (
          <div class="recruit-point">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>{point}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="recruit-message">
        <p>
          ビューティーブロウは「働きやすさ」を大切にしています。<br />
          完全週休2日、残業少なめ、有給取得率90%以上。<br />
          プライベートも充実させながら、美容のプロとして成長できる環境です。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="recruit-action">
        <a href="/recruit" class="btn-recruit">
          採用情報を見る
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .recruit {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f3f0 0%, #fff 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .recruit::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 60%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(173, 165, 139, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-width, 1120px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .recruit-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  
  .section-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .recruit-points {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .recruit-point {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .recruit-point svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .recruit-point span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .recruit-message {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .recruit-message p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .recruit-action {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .btn-recruit {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .btn-recruit:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(173, 165, 139, 0.3);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    
    .recruit-points {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>